                 val note = getColUnsafe.getNote(noteId).apply {
                     setTagsFromStr(getColUnsafe, tagsList.joinToString(","))
                 }
```

could use the following. But `Tags` would be better

```kotlin
tags.stringIterable().joinToString(",")
```


